{"nomor":104,"nama":"الهمزة","nama_latin":"Al-Humazah","jumlah_ayat":9,"tempat_turun":"mekah","arti":"Pengumpat","deskripsi":"Surat Al Humazah terdiri atas 9 ayat, termasuk golongan surat-surat Makkiyyah, diturunkan sesudah surat Al Qiyaamah. Dinamai <i>Al Humazah</i> (pengumpat) diambil dari perkataan <i>Humazah</i> yang terdapat pada ayat pertama surat ini.","audio":"https://cdn.equran.id/audio-full/Misyari-Rasyid-Al-Afasi/104.mp3","ayat":[{"id":6180,"surah":104,"nomor":1,"ar":"وَيْلٌ لِّكُلِّ هُمَزَةٍ لُّمَزَةٍۙ","tr":"Wailul likulli humazatil-lumazah(tin).","idn":"Celakalah setiap pengumpat lagi pencela"},{"id":6181,"surah":104,"nomor":2,"ar":" ۨالَّذِيْ جَمَعَ مَالًا وَّعَدَّدَهٗۙ","tr":"Allażī jama‘a mālaw wa ‘addadah(ū).","idn":"yang mengumpulkan harta dan menghitung-hitungnya."},{"id":6182,"surah":104,"nomor":3,"ar":"يَحْسَبُ اَنَّ مَالَهٗٓ اَخْلَدَهٗۚ","tr":"Yaḥsabu anna mālahū akhladah(ū).","idn":"Dia (manusia) mengira bahwa hartanya dapat mengekalkannya."},{"id":6183,"surah":104,"nomor":4,"ar":"كَلَّا لَيُنْۢبَذَنَّ فِى الْحُطَمَةِۖ","tr":"Kallā layumbażanna fil-ḥuṭamah(ti).","idn":"Sekali-kali tidak! Pasti dia akan dilemparkan ke dalam (neraka) Hutamah."},{"id":6184,"surah":104,"nomor":5,"ar":"وَمَآ اَدْرٰىكَ مَا الْحُطَمَةُ ۗ","tr":"Wa mā adrāka mal-ḥuṭamah(tu).","idn":"Tahukah kamu apakah (neraka) Hutamah?"},{"id":6185,"surah":104,"nomor":6,"ar":"نَارُ اللّٰهِ الْمُوْقَدَةُۙ","tr":"Nārullāhil-mūqadah(tu).","idn":"(Ia adalah) api (azab) Allah yang dinyalakan"},{"id":6186,"surah":104,"nomor":7,"ar":"الَّتِيْ تَطَّلِعُ عَلَى الْاَفْـِٕدَةِۗ","tr":"Allatī taṭṭali‘u ‘alal-af'idah(ti).","idn":"yang (membakar) naik sampai ke hati."},{"id":6187,"surah":104,"nomor":8,"ar":"اِنَّهَا عَلَيْهِمْ مُّؤْصَدَةٌۙ","tr":"Innahā ‘alaihim mu'ṣadah(tun).","idn":"Sesungguhnya dia (api itu) tertutup rapat (sebagai hukuman) atas mereka,"},{"id":6188,"surah":104,"nomor":9,"ar":"فِيْ عَمَدٍ مُّمَدَّدَةٍ ࣖ","tr":"Fī ‘amadim mumaddadah(tin).","idn":"(sedangkan mereka) diikat pad